{"title":"哈希表","uid":"52296d4e1e538f3ec200aa2ca9533c17","slug":"哈希表","date":"2021-08-09T04:01:28.000Z","updated":"2021-08-09T06:22:39.634Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/哈希表.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/theme/20210809.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"哈希表\"><a href=\"#哈希表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"哈希表\"></a>哈希表</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><code>哈希表</code>是一种数据结构，它使用哈希函数组织数据， 以支持<code>快速插入和搜索</code>.</p></blockquote>\n<p><b>哈希表的原理</b></p>\n<p>哈希表的关键思想是使用哈希函数<code>将键映射到储存桶</code>.(其实可以简单的对应数学函数的映射)</p>\n<ol>\n<li>当插入一个新的键时，哈希函数将决定该键应该分配到哪个桶中，并将该键储存在相应的桶中；</li>\n<li>如果需要搜索一个键的时候，哈希表将使用相同的哈希函数来查找对应的桶，并只在特定的桶中进行搜索；</li>\n</ol>\n<p><b>示例</b></p>\n<p>拟用<code>y = x % 4</code>作为哈希函数，其初始映射如下：</p>\n<p><img src=\"../images/blog/image-20210809122050690-1628482868473-1628482878091.png\" alt=\"image-20210809122050690\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><ol>\n<li>插入：我们通过哈希函数解析键，将它们映射到相应的桶中，比如把7分配给桶3；</li>\n<li>搜索：通过哈希函数解析键，并在相应的桶中搜索，比如搜索100，首先得到对应的桶0，然后再桶0中进行搜索；</li>\n</ol></blockquote>\n","text":"哈希表 哈希表是一种数据结构，它使用哈希函数组织数据， 以支持快速插入和搜索. 哈希表的原理 哈希表的关键思想是使用哈希函数将键映射到储存桶.(其实可以简单的对应数学函数的映射) 当插入一个新的键时，哈希函数将决定该键应该分配到哪个桶中，并将该键储存在相应的桶中； 如果需要搜索一...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":324,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"哈希表","slug":"哈希表","count":1,"path":"api/categories/哈希表.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hash table","slug":"hash-table","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hash-table.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%93%88%E5%B8%8C%E8%A1%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">哈希表</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Dominique Yiu","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/dominique-yiu/csdn/raw/master/theme/icon.png","link":"/","description":"There is only one heroism in the world, to see the world as it is and to love it. <br /> @ <b>realrealyiu@gmail.com</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Dominique-Yiu","twitter":"https://twitter.com/KingSwi39106371","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/whatever-36-86","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_49005782","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"2020高教社杯-C","uid":"8a7b21ee7893fa661a890526328e4199","slug":"2020高教社杯-C","date":"2021-07-19T09:30:38.000Z","updated":"2021-07-23T13:00:47.850Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2020高教社杯-C.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/theme/210723.jpg","text":"题意分析：银行通常根据信贷政策、企业的交易票据信息和上下游企业的影响力，向实力强、供求关系稳定的企业提供贷款，并可对信誉高、信贷风险小的企业居于利率优惠；银行首先根据企业的实力、信誉对其信贷风险进行评估，然后根据风险等因素来确定是否放贷及贷款额度、利率和期限等信贷策略； 银行信息...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbols